--- QuickSceneSetup Static Class Fix - 2026-03-04
+++ Assets/Scripts/Editor/QuickSceneSetup.cs

ISSUE:
======
ArgumentException: GetComponent requires that the requested component 
'GroundPlaneGenerator' derives from MonoBehaviour or Component or is an 
interface.

ROOT CAUSE:
===========
GroundPlaneGenerator and CeilingGenerator are STATIC CLASSES, not 
MonoBehaviour components. They cannot be added via AddComponent().

ERROR LOCATION:
===============
Assets/Scripts/Editor/QuickSceneSetup.cs line 127:
  AddComponentIfMissing(mazeTest, "Code.Lavos.Core.GroundPlaneGenerator");
  AddComponentIfMissing(mazeTest, "Code.Lavos.Core.CeilingGenerator");

FIX APPLIED:
============
1. Removed GroundPlaneGenerator and CeilingGenerator from AddCoreComponents()
2. Updated component count: 13 → 11 components
3. Updated debug log to clarify FpsMazeTest handles ground/ceiling
4. Added comment explaining static classes

CHANGES:
========

